Accessing Gemini via KNIME

Install the required extensions:

Search for the required extensions. Select them and press Next. Once installation is complete, press finish. Once installation is complete, restart KNIME.

Set up the workflow

Credential Configuration Node:

Enter API key in Password. Leave Username empty.

Gemini LLM Selector:

Select the desired model. Choose lite for conserving tokens
